Nick Kounis, head of macro research 
at ABN Amro in Amsterdam, says European Central Bank President 
Mario Draghi is making "very subtle" efforts to weaken the euro.
Kounis talks with Bloomberg's Michael McKee on Bloomberg Radio's
"Bloomberg - The First Word."
